{
  "_comment": "Scoped field mapping (Task 11). Two top-level directions — crmToMarketo (CRM authoritative) and marketoToCrm (Marketo authoritative, narrow per spec §Operational Behaviour). Each entry has shape { source, type, entitySet?, optionSet?, derivation? }. type ∈ text|choice|lookup|boolean|guid|derived. Choice/lookup/derived entries are declared here; their runtime resolvers are Tasks 11b/12/13. Until then, choice and lookup entries pass through as text.",
